      <title>莫迪执政联盟险胜 8% 印度增长计划面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-s-narrow-election-win-will-make-it-harder-to-meet-india-s-economy-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的政党在选举中未能赢得多数支持，其雄心勃勃的经济增长目标面临风险，这使得他更加依赖联合政府来推动艰难的经济改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/modi-s-narrow-election-win-will-make-it-harder-to-meet-india-s-economy-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:26:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>希腊举行史上最长海军演习阻止俄罗斯石油输送</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/greece-deters-russian-oil-transfers-with-longest-navy-drills-yet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[希腊海军在该国沿海附近的一片水域恢复演习，有效阻止了俄罗斯利用该地区进行油轮石油转运的能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/greece-deters-russian-oil-transfers-with-longest-navy-drills-yet</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:20:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亨特·拜登的律师称，他没有“故​​意”撒谎购买枪支</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hunter-biden-didn-t-knowingly-lie-to-buy-gun-his-lawyer-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亨特·拜登的律师周二在特拉华州联邦法院的审判开庭陈述中告诉陪审团，亨特·拜登在 2018 年填写购枪表格并勾选“未吸毒”的方框时并没有故意撒谎。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/hunter-biden-didn-t-knowingly-lie-to-buy-gun-his-lawyer-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登采取措施封锁边境，避免选举前出现激增</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-moves-to-seal-border-in-bid-to-avoid-surge-before-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登出台了一系列措施，旨在遏制庇护申请，并阻止今年夏天跨境人数激增，这是解决其国内最大弱点之一的一项具有政治争议的举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-moves-to-seal-border-in-bid-to-avoid-surge-before-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国政党被指在重大经济风险问题上“回避现实”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/uk-parties-accused-of-avoiding-reality-over-big-economic-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国两大顶级智库警告称，随着选举因小额承诺而陷入激烈争论，英国两大政党均拒绝解决公共服务的长期问题和迫在眉睫的经济风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/uk-parties-accused-of-avoiding-reality-over-big-economic-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 16:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥大选后，AMLO 推出医疗诊所资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/amlo-rolls-out-health-clinic-funding-following-mexico-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔周二宣布了一项加强墨西哥医疗保健的计划，旨在解决其政党在选举中取得压倒性胜利后选民对其政府提出的一项关键投诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/amlo-rolls-out-health-clinic-funding-following-mexico-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 15:21:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非主要反对党对联合政府抱有乐观态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非主要反对党民主联盟领导人表示，投资者对该党将与非国大达成联合执政协议组建下一届政府的乐观态度没有错，该党愿意进行以国家利益为优先的谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/south-african-election-main-opposition-sees-room-for-optimism-on-coalition</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:54:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法拉奇在英国竞选活动开始时喝了奶昔</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国脱欧的策划者奈杰尔·法拉奇在狂欢节般的氛围中发起了竞选克拉克顿议会席位的行动，数百人聚集到埃塞克斯海滨，承诺颠覆英国政治秩序。但并非一切都如这位新任改革英国领袖所愿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/farage-draws-crowds-to-clacton-and-gets-drenched-in-beverage</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 14:52:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称有理由质疑内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统乔·拜登在周二接受《时代》杂志采访时表示，人们有理由得出这样的结论：以色列总理本雅明·内塔尼亚胡延长加沙战争是出于他自己的政治考虑，并且不排除派遣美军保卫台湾。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-04/biden-every-reason-to-question-if-netanyahu-prolonging-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 04 Jun 2024 13:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
